是大偶数, 则有:\u003cbr\u003e \u003cimg src=\"https://www.zhihu.com/equation?tex=P_%7Bx%7D+%28x+%2C+x%5E%7B%5Cfrac%7B1%7D%7B10%7D%7D%29+-+%5Cfrac%7B1%7D%7B2%7D+%5Csum_%7Bx%5E%5Cfrac%7B1%7D%7B10%7D+%3C+r+%5Cleq+x%5E%7B%5Cfrac%7B1%7D%7B3%7D%7D%7D+P_%7Bx%7D+%28x+%2C+p+%2C+x%5E%7B%5Cfrac+%7B1%7D+%7B10%7D%7D%29+%5Cgeq+%5Cfrac+%7B2.6408+x+C_%7Bx%7D%7D+%7B%28%5Clog+x%29%5E%7B2%7D%7D\" alt=\"P_{x} (x , x^{\\frac{1}{10}}) - \\frac{1}{2} \\sum_{x^\\frac{1}{10} \u0026lt; r \\leq x^{\\frac{1}{3}}} P_{x} (x , p , x^{\\frac {1} {10}}) \\geq \\frac {2.6408 x C_{x}} {(\\log x)^{2}}\" eeimg=\"1\"\u003e \u003cbr\u003e 其中  \u003cimg src=\"https://www.zhihu.com/equation?tex=%5Cdisplaystyle%7BC_%7Bx%7D+%3D+%5Cprod_%7B%7Bp%7Cx%7D%5Cvee%7Bp+%3E+2%7D%7D+%5Cfrac+%7Bp+-+1%7D+%7Bp+-+2%7D+%5Cprod_%7Bp+%3E+2%7D+%5Cleft%281+-+%5Cfrac+%7B1%7D+%7B%28p+-+1%29%5E%7B2%7D%7D%5Cright%29%7D\" alt=\"\\displaystyle{C_{x} = \\prod_{{p|x}\\vee{p \u0026gt; 2}} \\frac {p - 1} {p - 2} \\prod_{p \u0026gt; 2} \\left(1 - \\frac {1} {(p - 1)^{2}}\\right)}\" eeimg=\"1\"\u003e .\u003c/blockquote\u003e\u003cp\u003e这个公式和哥德巴赫猜想密切相关\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e下面是这个结论的证明, 希望你能指出证明的不足之处并加以改进!\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e我个人感激不尽, 放假\u003cb\u003e保证送你去清华吃饭\u003c/b\u003e, 不过我很怀疑清华数学系附近有没有好吃的食堂...\u003c/p\u003e\u003chr\u003e\u003cp\u003e取 \u003cimg src=\"https://www.zhihu.com/equation?tex=%5Cdisplaystyle%7Br%28p%29+%3D+%5Cfrac+%7Bp%7D+%7Bp+-+1%7D+%2C+K+%3D+x+%2C+Z+%3D+x%5E%7B%5Cfrac+%7B1%7D+%7B10%7D%7D%7D\" alt=\"\\displaystyle{r(p) = \\frac {p} {p - 1} , K = x , Z = x^{\\frac {1} {10}}}\" eeimg=\"1\"\u003e, 我们有\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://www.zhihu.com/equation?tex=%5Cbegin%7Baligned%7D+%5CGamma_%7Bx%7D+%28x%5E%7B%5Cfrac+%7B1%7D+%7B10%7D%7D%29+%26%3D%5Cfrac+%7Bx%7D+%7B%5Cvarphi+%28x%29%7D+%5Cprod_%7Bp%5Cnmid+x%7D+%5Cfrac+%7B1+-+%5Cfrac+%7B1%7D+%7Bp+-+1%7D%7D+%7B1+-+%5Cfrac+%7B1%7D+%7Bp%7D%7D+%5Cfrac+%7Be%5E%7B-+r%7D%7D+%7B%5Clog+x%5E%7B%5Cfrac+%7B1%7D+%7B10%7D%7D%7D+%5Cleft%5C%7B1+%2B+O%5Cleft%28%5Cfrac+%7B1%7D+%7B%5Clog+x%7D%5Cright%29+%5Cright%5C%7D%5C%5C+%26%3D+%5Cfrac+%7Bx%7D+%7B%5Cvarphi+%28x%29%7D%5Cprod_%7B%7Bp%7Cx%7D%5Cvee%7Bp+%3E+2%7D%7D%5Cfrac+%7B%28p+-+1%29%5E%7B2%7D%7D+%7Bp+%28p+-+2%29%7D%5Cprod_%7Bp+%3E+2%7D+%5Cleft%281+-+%5Cfrac+%7B1%7D+%7B%28p+-+1%29%5E%7B2%7D%7D%5Cright%29+%5Cfrac+%7Bc%5E%7B-+r%7D%7D+%7B%5Clog+x%5E%7B%5Cfrac+%7B1%7D+%7B10%7D%7D%7D+%5Cleft%5C%7B1+%2B+O+%5Cleft%28%5Cfrac+%7B1%7D%7B%5Clog+x%7D%5Cright%29+%5Cright%5C%7D%5C%5C+%26%3D+%5Cfrac+%7B20+e%5E%7B-+%5Cgamma%7D+C_%7Bx%7D%7D+%7B%5Clog+x%7D%5Cleft%5C%7B1+%2B+O+%5Cleft%28%5Cfrac+%7B1%7D%7B%5Clog+x%7D%5Cright%29+%5Cright%5C%7D+%5Cend%7Baligned%7D\" alt=\"\\begin{aligned} \\Gamma_{x} (x^{\\frac {1} {10}}) \u0026amp;=\\frac {x} {\\varphi (x)} \\prod_{p\\nmid x} \\frac {1 - \\frac {1} {p - 1}} {1 - \\frac {1} {p}} \\frac {e^{- r}} {\\log x^{\\frac {1} {10}}} \\left\\{1 + O\\left(\\frac {1} {\\log x}\\right) \\right\\}\\\\ \u0026amp;= \\frac {x} {\\varphi (x)}\\prod_{{p|x}\\vee{p \u0026gt; 2}}\\frac {(p - 1)^{2}} {p (p - 2)}\\prod_{p \u0026gt; 2} \\left(1 - \\frac {1} {(p - 1)^{2}}\\right) \\frac {c^{- r}} {\\log x^{\\frac {1} {10}}} \\left\\{1 + O \\left(\\frac {1}{\\log x}\\right) \\right\\}\\\\ \u0026amp;= \\frac {20 e^{- \\gamma} C_{x}} {\\log x}\\left\\{1 + O \\left(\\frac {1}{\\log x}\\right) \\right\\} \\end{aligned}\" eeimg=\"1\"\u003e \u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e其中 \u003cimg src=\"https://www.zhihu.com/equation?tex=%5Cgamma\" alt=\"\\gamma\" eeimg=\"1\"\u003e 是 Euler 常数. \u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e取  \u003cimg src=\"https://www.zhihu.com/equation?tex=%5Cxi%5E%7B2%7D+%3D+x%5E%7B%5Cfrac+%7B1%7D+%7B2%7D+-+%5Cepsilon%7D+%2C+q+%3D+1+%2C++z+%3D+x%5E%7B%5Cfrac+%7B1%7D%7B10%7D%7D\" alt=\"\\xi^{2} = x^{\\frac {1} {2} - \\epsilon} , q = 1 ,  z = x^{\\frac {1}{10}}\" eeimg=\"1\"\u003e , 则由上式可知, 当 \u003cimg src=\"https://www.zhihu.com/equation?tex=x\" alt=\"x\" eeimg=\"1\"\u003e 很大时, 有: \u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://www.zhihu.com/equation?tex=%5Cbegin%7Baligned%7D+P_%7Bx%7D+%28x+%2C+x%5E%7B%5Cfrac+%7B1%7D+%7B10%7D%7D%29++%26%5Cgeq+%5Cfrac+%7B2+%281+-+%5Csqrt+%7Be%7D%29+e%5E%7B-+r%7D+x+C_%7Bx%7D+f+%285%29%7D+%7B%28%5Clog+x%29+%28%5Clog+x%5E%7B%5Cfrac+%7B1%7D+%7B10%7D%7D%29%7D+%5C%5C+%26%5Cgeq+%5Cleft%5C%7B%5Cfrac+%7B8+%281+-+%5Csqrt+%7Be%7D%29+x+C_%7Bx%7D%7D+%7B%28%5Clog+x%29%5E%7B2%7D%7D+%5Cright%5C%7D%5Ccdot+%5Cleft%5C%7B%5Clog+4+%2B+%5Cint_%7B3%7D%5E%7B4%7D+%5Cfrac+%7Bd+u%7D+%7Bu%7D+%5Cint_%7B2%7D%5E%7Bn+-+1%7D+%5Cfrac+%7B%5Clog+%28t+-+1%29%7D+%7Bt%7D+%5Cmathrm%7Bd%7D+t+%5Cright%5C%7D+%5Cend%7Baligned%7D\" alt=\"\\begin{aligned} P_{x} (x , x^{\\frac {1} {10}})  \u0026amp;\\geq \\frac {2 (1 - \\sqrt {e}) e^{- r} x C_{x} f (5)} {(\\log x) (\\log x^{\\frac {1} {10}})} \\\\ \u0026amp;\\geq \\left\\{\\frac {8 (1 - \\sqrt {e}) x C_{x}} {(\\log x)^{2}} \\right\\}\\cdot \\left\\{\\log 4 + \\int_{3}^{4} \\frac {d u} {u} \\int_{2}^{n - 1} \\frac {\\log (t - 1)} {t} \\mathrm{d} t \\right\\} \\end{aligned}\" eeimg=\"1\"\u003e \u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e再取  \u003cimg src=\"https://www.zhihu.com/equation?tex=%5Cxi%5E%7B2%7D+%3D+%5Cdfrac%7Bx%5E%7B%5Cfrac+%7B1%7D+%7B2%7D+-+%5Cepsilon%7D%7D%7Bp%7D+%2C+q+%3D+p+%2C++z+%3D+x%5E%7B%5Cfrac+%7B1%7D%7B10%7D%7D\" alt=\"\\xi^{2} = \\dfrac{x^{\\frac {1} {2} - \\epsilon}}{p} , q = p ,  z = x^{\\frac {1}{10}}\" eeimg=\"1\"\u003e , 我们有\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://www.zhihu.com/equation?tex=%5Cbegin%7Baligned%7D+%5Csum_%7Bx%5E%5Cfrac%7B1%7D%7B10%7D+%3C+r+%5Cleq+x%5E%7B%5Cfrac%7B1%7D%7B3%7D%7D%7D+P_%7Bx%7D+%28x+%2C+p+%2C+x%5E%7B%5Cfrac+%7B1%7D+%7B10%7D%7D%29+%26%5Cleq%5Cleft%5C%7B%5Cfrac+%7B20+%281+%2B+%5Csqrt+%7Be%7D%29+e%5E%7B-+r%7D+x+C_%7Br%7D%7D+%7B%28%5Clog+x%29%5E%7B2%7D%7D+%5Cright%5C%7D+%5Cleft%5C%7B%5Csum_%7Bx%5E%5Cfrac%7B1%7D%7B10%7D+%3C+r+%5Cleq+x%5E%7B%5Cfrac%7B1%7D%7B5%7D%7D%7D%5Cleft%28%5Cfrac+%7B2+c%5E%7Br%7D%7D+%7Bp%7D%5Cright%29%5Ccdot+%5Cleft%281+%2B+%5Cint_%7B2%7D%5E%7B4+-+%5Cfrac+%7B100+%5Clog+p%7D+%7B%5Clog+x%7D%7D+%5Cfrac+%7B%5Clog+%28t+-+1%29%7D+%7Bt%7D+%5Cmathrm%7Bd%7Dt%5Crig